        <title>Updates to the Frontity Contact Form 7 package</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[kasper]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Hi,</p>
<p>I just released v.0.2.3 for the Frontity cf7 package. This version has mostly been focused on bugs, keeping up with the latest versions of Frontity and the plugin itself.</p>
<p>But I have also added a couple of new features, focusing on accessibility. Now the input and textfields support id. And I have also made sure that empty attributes doesn’t get injected into the html.</p>
<p>Here is an example on the effect of that. Before the update:<br>
</p><div class="lightbox-wrapper"><a class="lightbox" href="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/original/2X/9/963182f2822737de250be8ad51f06451ecb84674.png" data-download-href="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/963182f2822737de250be8ad51f06451ecb84674" title="cf7before"><img src="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/9/963182f2822737de250be8ad51f06451ecb84674_2_690x337.png" alt="cf7before" data-base62-sha1="lqFHj0NeIqPa1jyW7x3iLYkDyHW" width="690" height="337" srcset="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/9/963182f2822737de250be8ad51f06451ecb84674_2_690x337.png, https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/9/963182f2822737de250be8ad51f06451ecb84674_2_1035x505.png 1.5x, https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/9/963182f2822737de250be8ad51f06451ecb84674_2_1380x674.png 2x" data-small-upload="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/9/963182f2822737de250be8ad51f06451ecb84674_2_10x10.png"></a></div><p></p>
<p>Same form, after the update:<br>
</p><div class="lightbox-wrapper"><a class="lightbox" href="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/original/2X/e/e36c2aa2256736794c4626b90e3ab3208a062462.png" data-download-href="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/e36c2aa2256736794c4626b90e3ab3208a062462" title="cf7after"><img src="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/e/e36c2aa2256736794c4626b90e3ab3208a062462_2_690x337.png" alt="cf7after" data-base62-sha1="wrS89AMEXQmc2RZVsoQCR55ccHU" width="690" height="337" srcset="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/e/e36c2aa2256736794c4626b90e3ab3208a062462_2_690x337.png, https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/e/e36c2aa2256736794c4626b90e3ab3208a062462_2_1035x505.png 1.5x, https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/e/e36c2aa2256736794c4626b90e3ab3208a062462_2_1380x674.png 2x" data-small-upload="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/e/e36c2aa2256736794c4626b90e3ab3208a062462_2_10x10.png"></a></div><p></p>
